emand好勁. 我突然對中共糧食問題有啲興趣.<br />\n<br />\n我知道豬瘟冇消失過,仲吹話變左傳人. 蝗蟲我唔清楚有幾大獲. 但水霸噴水會唔會影響食糧供應? 有幾多? 同人玩制裁又唔買人地肉，又影響幾多?<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打一齊集思廣益睇下佢地糧食問題有冇出問題?"},{"pid":"b79799a1eb378247ece0571335bff16564cbfd2e","tid":2100071,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:40:08.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n上面有好多韭菜"},{"pid":"2ad9cf9a7ee53232d1a141b4d68341215f18a9e5","tid":2100071,"uid":361025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:40:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"247ad78ee5317c6f049b584530b79a83100024f3","tid":2100071,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ad9cf9a7ee53232d1a141b4d68341215f18a9e5","tid":2100071,"uid":361025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:40:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"收歸國有"},{"pid":"1900d835081b1e14067399278484ec261cba24db","tid":2100071,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T19:09:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-07-06/4757048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-07-06%2F4757048&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=ba28f166\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-07-06/4757048</a><br />\n就咁search字眼得番大紀元講"}]}